## Folder Structure
```
.raw/          → drop source files here, then ingest
wiki/          → hot.md · index.md · log.md · sources · entities · concepts
00_INBOX/      → nightly agent input (Notion + disk sync)
10_NOTES/      → atomic notes
20_PROJECTS/   → your projects
30_PEOPLE/     → people
40_RESOURCES/  → articles, references
50_DAILY/      → morning reports (YYYY-MM-DD-morning.md)
60_ACTIONS/    → actions.md · product-opportunities.md
  decisions/   → decision archive (YYYY-MM-DD-topic.md) — pre-decision brief reads this
  patterns/    → weekly/monthly pattern reports (nightly agent writes)
  business-edge/ → BUSINESS-EDGE.md (known weaknesses + edge definition)
70_ARCHIVE/    → processed INBOX
MEMORY/        → WORK · KNOWLEDGE · LEARNING
```

## Compounding Intelligence

Every important decision → save as `60_ACTIONS/decisions/YYYY-MM-DD-topic.md`.
Template: `60_ACTIONS/decisions/_TEMPLATE.md`

Use the `/api/pre-decision` endpoint in the dashboard for pre-decision briefs:
past decisions + known weaknesses + pattern analysis → briefing before deciding.

`BUSINESS-EDGE.md` → updated by nightly agent, tracks strengths and weaknesses.

